timelineItems.text: Waiting for Bobby to have a clean sheet for … two saves? Oh is that three? #NERevs

timelineItems.name: Andrew Villegas
timelineItems.text: It's not the referee's fault the #Rapids96 have no depth. He was poor, but Pablo has squeezed and squeezed. Depth orange is dry.

timelineItems.comment: Attempt saved. Steve Neumann (New England Revolution) right footed shot from outside the box is saved in the top right corner. Assisted by Daigo Kobayashi.
Corner,  New England Revolution. Conceded by Clint Irwin.

timelineItems.name: Christopher Brown
timelineItems.text: WHO YOU GONNA CALL?! STREAK BUSTERS!!! #NERevs #StreakBusters http://t.co/j8V4kPlbck

timelineItems.comment: Foul by Daigo Kobayashi (New England Revolution).
Dillon Powers (Colorado Rapids) wins a free kick in the attacking half.

timelineItems.name: HV Spicer
timelineItems.text: Hold the phone. I think my heart has stopped. A #NERevs win?! #itsabouttime #welcomebackboys

timelineItems.comment: Attempt saved. Patrick Mullins (New England Revolution) left footed shot from outside the box is saved in the bottom left corner. Assisted by Daigo Kobayashi with a through ball.

timelineItems.name: Rowena Kim
timelineItems.text: #NERevs @NErebellion @MidnightRiders STAND UP!!!! @NERevolution WIN 3-0! @FootyJedi @kbstrgrl @MelvilleArtie http://t.co/gyg5oL1gRD

timelineItems.name: Chris Bianchi
timelineItems.text: Well, that couldn’t one end quickly enough. Tied for most lopsided loss of season at 3-0. Simply a brutal performance all around…

timelineItems.name: Andrew Villegas
timelineItems.text: Totally deserved loss. New England is not Brazil, traveling sucks, but get used to it. #Rapids96

timelineItems.comment: Second Half ends, New England Revolution 3, Colorado Rapids 0.
